{"tid":1437514,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲國會議員：中國稱霸野心有如納粹","createTime":"2019-08-09T14:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:19:22.000Z","uid":270374,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"638ef87eb351dc9ce34a6d2aafaad35677a50ccb","tid":1437514,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:20:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n澳洲國會情報和安全聯合委員會主席海斯迪（Andrew Hastie）八日警告，中國企圖稱霸世界的野心，有如掀起二戰的納粹德國，澳洲的主權和自由將受到北京前所未有的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n「一如法國人，澳洲（人）也沒能認清，我們的獨裁鄰邦（指中國）變得有多靈活。」馬奇諾防線並未擋住德軍入侵，納粹最後改從北方進攻；「下一個十年我國的民主價值、經濟、同盟和安全將面臨考驗，這在澳洲歷史上前所未見。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1309422?fbclid=IwAR3VedlJ4Xykmw8IwxqpfMKg13hnTkGhxhG4H9-ZdSSCRexa6u_1iIVMUu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1309422%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3VedlJ4Xykmw8IwxqpfMKg13hnTkGhxhG4H9-ZdSSCRexa6u_1iIVMUu8&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=4c4e1a8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1309422%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3VedlJ4Xykmw8IwxqpfMKg13hnTkGhxhG4H9-ZdSSCRexa6u_1iIVMUu8&h=dea819b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1309422?fbclid=IwAR3VedlJ4Xykmw8IwxqpfMKg13hnTkGhxhG4H9-ZdSSCRexa6u_1iIVMUu8</a>"},{"pid":"133cb6eaaab51f85b3dede7d6a368ecb4001c5db","tid":1437514,"uid":33614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"638ef87eb351dc9ce34a6d2aafaad35677a50ccb","tid":1437514,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:20:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n澳洲國會情報和安全聯合委員會主席海斯迪（Andrew Hastie）八日警告，中國企圖稱霸世界的野心，有如掀起二戰的納粹德國，澳洲的主權和自由將受到北京前所未有的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n「一如法國人，澳洲（人）也沒能認清，我們的獨裁鄰邦（指中國）變得有多靈活。」馬奇諾防線並未擋住德軍入侵，納粹最後改從北方進攻；「下一個十年我國的民主價值、經濟、同盟和安全將面臨考驗，這在澳洲歷史上前所未見。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1309422?fbclid=IwAR3VedlJ4Xykmw8IwxqpfMKg13hnTkGh